                    </div>
                    <span>I enjoyed this book from beginning to end. Anytime I had a moment to read, I reached for this book and was absorbed by the story. I'm ready to read more books by Princess Sultana. <P>This is a fascinating first-hand look at what women have to go through and live under in countries where life is ruled by men. There isn't any way out of that life except by following or being forced to follow the cruel or oppressive conditions. <P>This book follows the princess from her girlhood to an arranged marriage and its consequences. <P>Highly recommended to anyone who is interested in women's rights, their lives and dark secrets in different countries.</span>
                  
